# Node.js Application

This is a Node.js application that allows users to save text and images, with support for private entries and a passcode-protected private section.

---

## **Features**
- Save text entries with a heading and description.
- Upload images.
- Search entries by text or date.
- Private section protected by a passcode.
- Responsive and modern UI.

---

## **Prerequisites**
Before running the application, ensure you have the following installed:
- [Node.js](https://nodejs.org/) (v18 or higher)
- [npm](https://www.npmjs.com/) (comes with Node.js)
- [Docker](https://www.docker.com/) (optional, for containerization)
- [MongoDB](https://www.mongodb.com/) (or a MongoDB connection string)

---